The '''Holder of the Laws''' was an [[Time/Legends|archaic]] title given to [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] who fulfilled the role of a [[Judge/Legends|judge]]. Around [[3956 BBY]], [[Worrroznor]] held the position within [[Rwookrrorro/Legends|Rwookrrorro]] village.<ref name="KOTOR">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''</ref>

